description:
&lt;p&gt;A fantastic opportunity has arisen for an enthusiastic and motivated individual to provide a Supervisory and Medical Secretarial role to the Ophthalmology department based mainly in the Sussex Eye Hospital, Brighton with occasional working at Princess Royal Hospital, Haywards Heath. Accountable to the Secretarial Service Manager, you will work closely with clinicians and directorate teams to deliver a first class secretarial service.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidate will require excellent organisational skills, demonstrate the ability to work independently, using their own initiative and be willing to be adaptable and flexible to meet the needs of the Service.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an experienced Medical secretary &amp; Supervisor to provide and be responsible for the management of the secretarial team, providing leadership and support, prioritising work as required on a daily basis.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please address the knowledge, skills and experience of the Person Specification clearly in your application as this will be the basis used for those selected for interview. Please ensure you have read the Job Description before applying.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Name Katherine Aspindale&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Job title Secretarial Service Manager&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email address katherine.aspindale@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Telephone number 01273 696955 Ext 64259&lt;/p&gt;
